#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_parquet.read_parquet:1 of
msgid "Load a parquet object from the file path, returning a DataFrame."
msgstr "从文件路径加载一个 parquet 对象，返回一个 DataFrame。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.read_parquet.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_parquet.read_parquet:3 of
msgid ""
"Any valid string path is acceptable. The string could be a URL. For file "
"URLs, a host is expected. A local file could be: "
"``file://localhost/path/to/table.parquet``. A file URL can also be a path"
" to a directory that contains multiple partitioned parquet files. Both "
"pyarrow and fastparquet support paths to directories as well as file "
"URLs. A directory path could be: ``file://localhost/path/to/tables``. By "
"file-like object, we refer to objects with a ``read()`` method, such as a"
" file handler (e.g. via builtin ``open`` function) or ``StringIO``."
msgstr ""
"任何有效的字符串路径都可以接受。该字符串可以是一个 URL。对于文件 URL，"
"需要指定主机。一个本地文件可以是：``file://localhost/path/to/table."
"parquet``。一个文件 URL 也可以是指向包含多个分区 parquet 文件的目录的路径"
"。pyarrow 和 fastparquet 都支持目录路径和文件 URL。一个目录路径可以是：``"
"file://localhost/path/to/tables``。所谓类文件对象，我们指的是具有 ``read("
")`` 方法的对象，例如文件句柄（例如通过内置的 ``open`` 函数）或 ``StringIO"
"``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_parquet.read_parquet:14 of
msgid "Parquet library to use. The default behavior is to try 'pyarrow',"
msgstr "使用的 Parquet 库。默认行为是尝试使用 'pyarrow'，"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_parquet.read_parquet:16
#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_parquet.read_parquet:29 of
msgid "Options for storage connection."
msgstr "存储连接的选项。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_parquet.read_parquet:18 of
msgid "If not None, only these columns will be read from the file."
msgstr "如果非 None，则只从文件中读取这些列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_parquet.read_parquet:20 of
msgid ""
"if True, each row group correspond to a chunk. if False, each file "
"correspond to a chunk. Only available for 'pyarrow' engine."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则每个行组对应一个 chunk；如果为 False，则每个文件对应一个 "
"chunk。仅适用于 'pyarrow' 引擎。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_parquet.read_parquet:24 of
msgid ""
"If index_col not specified, ensure range index incremental, gain a "
"slightly better performance if setting False."
msgstr ""
"如果未指定 index_col，则确保范围索引递增，设置为 False 时可获得稍好的性能"
"。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_parquet.read_parquet:27 of
msgid ""
"Back-end data type applied to the resultant DataFrame (still "
"experimental)."
msgstr "应用于结果 DataFrame 的后端数据类型（仍处于实验阶段）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_parquet.read_parquet:31 of
msgid "Scale that real memory occupation divided with raw file size."
msgstr "实际内存占用与原始文件大小的比例。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_parquet.read_parquet:33 of
msgid "Merge small files whose size is small."
msgstr "合并尺寸较小的小文件。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_parquet.read_parquet:35 of
msgid "Any additional kwargs are passed to the engine."
msgstr "任何额外的 kwargs 都会传递给引擎。"

